\v 2 Ophikisana loSomandla uza\add m\add*qondisa yini? Osola uNkulunkulu kakuphendule\x + 33.13.\x*.
\p
\v 3 UJobe waseyiphendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi:
\p
\v 4 Khangela, ngiphansi; ngingakuphendula \add ngithi\add*ni\x + 42.6. Nah. 1.14. Ezra 9.6.\x*? Ngibeka isandla sami emlonyeni wami\x + Hlab. 39.9. Hlu. 18.19.\x*.
\v 5 Ngikhulumile kanye, kodwa kangiyikuphendula\x + 9.3. Hlab. 62.11.\x*; kumbe kabili, kodwa kangiyikuqhubeka\x + 9.3. Hlab. 62.11.\x*.
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* ibonakalisa amandla ayo
\p
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimphendula uJobe isesivunguzaneni yathi\x + 38.1.\x*:
\p
\v 7 Bopha khathesi ukhalo lwakho njengendoda\x + 38.3.\x*; ngizakubuza, ubusungazisa\x + 38.3. 42.4.\x*.
\v 8 Isibili, uzachitha isahlulelo sami yini\x + Hlab. 51.4. Roma 3.4. Hlab. 50.21.\x*? Ungilahle, ukuze ube ngolungileyo yini\x + 32.2. 35.2.\x*?
\v 9 Njalo ulengalo yini njengoNkulunkulu? Kumbe ungaduma yini ngelizwi njengaye\x + 37.4.\x*?
\v 10 Khathesi zicecise ngobukhosi lokuphakama, uzembese ngodumo lenkazimulo\x + Hlab. 104.1. Hlab. 93.1.\x*.
\v 11 Usabalalise intukuthelo zolaka lwakho\x + 21.30.\x*, ukhangele wonke ozigqajayo, umthobise\x + Isa. 2.12. Dan. 4.37.\x*.
\v 12 Khangela wonke ozigqajayo\x + Isa. 2.12. Dan. 4.37.\x*, umehlisele phansi\x + Isa. 2.12. Dan. 4.37.\x*, unyathelele phansi ababi endaweni yabo\x + 36.20.\x*.
\v 13 Ubafihle bonke\x + Isa. 2.10.\x* ethulini\x + 17.16. 21.26.\x*\x + Isa. 2.10.\x*, ubophe ubuso babo ngasese.
\v 14 Khona lami ngizavuma kuwe, ukuthi isandla sakho sokunene singakusindisa\x + Hlab. 98.1. Isa. 59.16. 63.5.\x*.
\v 15 Ake ukhangele imvubu engayenza kanye lawe; idla utshani njengenkabi\x + Hlab. 104.14.\x*.
\v 16 Ake ukhangele, amandla ayo asekhalweni lwayo, lokuqina kwayo kusemisipheni yesisu sayo.
\v 17 Iyagobisa umsila wayo njengomsedari; imisipha yemilenze yayo yelukene\x + Lilo 1.14.\x*.
\v 18 Amathambo ayo a\add njeng\add*empompi zethusi, amathambo ayo anjengemigoqo yensimbi.
\v 19 Ingeyokuqala\x + Amos 6.1,6. Zaga 8.22.\x* yezindlela zikaNkulunkulu\x + 26.14.\x*; owayenzayo wasondeza inkemba yayo.
\v 20 Ngoba intaba ziyayivezela ukudla, lapho okudlala khona inyamazana zonke zeganga.
\v 21 Ilala phansi kwesihlahla esiluhlaza, ekusithekeni kwemihlanga lamaxhaphozi\x + 8.11 Hez. 47.11.\x*.
\v 22 Izihlahla eziluhlaza ziyayisibekela \add ngo\add*mthunzi wazo; imidubu yesifula iyayiphahla\x + Levi 23.40. Hlab. 137.2. Isa. 15.7. 44.4.\x*.
\v 23 Khangela, umfula uya\add yi\add*cindezela, kayiphangisi\x + Dute. 20.3.\x*; ilesibindi lanxa iJordani ingaphuphumela emlonyeni wayo\x + 38.8.\x*.
\v 24 Ongayibamba yini ngamehlo ayo? Ongahlaba yini amakhala \add ayo\add* ngemijibila?